adequate incentive such as rendering a specific offer, the purchaser and/or recipient of the offer, will use this key to personally identify himself before the system, namely by means of a proper site on the Internet, through telephone line, SMS, MMS, WAP, among others. The present invention describes a system, database and co-related methods allowing the said functionality. By means of this identification it is possible to convert generic product and/or content purchase and/or offering, either with or without a social responsibility parameter, into totally identified transactions, thus generating information and allowing its validation and promotion.</p></abstract></us-patent-application>